title: Joel Embiid Crushes Raptors With Crazy Game-Winner
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss Joel Embiid’s epic game-winner, Celtics put the clamps on KD and Kyrie, DeMar DeRozan drops a monster 40-piece in win over Bucks, Bucks chances without Khris Middleton, best fit for Deebo Samuel next season, plus Shohei Ohtani’s ridiculous performance against Astros. All that and more!!!
